  "title": "[Fast Hiring!] x6 Retail Assistant-Islandwide | Mobile/Fashion/Sport/Chocolate",
  "description": "<p><strong>Summary</strong></p><ul><li><p>Fix Basic $2300-$2800</p></li><li><p>Commission+AWS</p></li><li><p>Fast hiring process!</p></li><li><p>Islandwide, Multiple Headcount</p></li><li><p>Well-known brand with stability</p></li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Provide friendly and helpful customer service, assisting customers with product inquiries and selections.</p></li><li><p>Handle cashier duties including processing payments, issuing receipts, and managing returns or exchanges.</p></li><li><p>Maintain store cleanliness, organization, and product display standards.</p></li><li><p>Replenish stock on shelves and monitor inventory levels to ensure product availability.</p></li><li><p>Assist in receiving, unpacking, and tagging new stock deliveries.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Entry level are welcome to apply, proper training will be provided.</p></li></ul><p>To Apply, kindly click on the \"APPLY NOW\" button</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Staffking Pte Ltd (20C0358) | Lee Zi Qing (R25126986)</p><p>EA License No: 20C0358</p>",
